name: Byzantine Roman Crate
description: Founders get all items in this crate for free and should not purchase this crate. A collection of Roman themed cosmetic items for the Byzantines. Equip your units with Scutum and Gladius, lead your empire from the Roman Palace and show your might with a Roman banner. Also includes 3 Roman themed in-game avatars.

name: Emperor's Chest
description: A chest containing 4 random in-game cosmetic items. Items have the following rarities: Common, Rare, Epic, Legendary. One item is guaranteed to be Rare or better. The weighted chances for every item are as follows: - A Conqueror's Chest contains 4 items, of which one is guaranteed to be Rare or better. The chances (calculated per-item) are as follows: Common: 52.5%, Rare: 35%, Epic: 9.75%, Legendary: 2.75%.

name: French Mythic Crate
description: A collection of mythic themed cosmetic items for the French. Equip larger than life swords, shields and lances! Build your kingdom from a brand new Gothic Town Center and show your might with a Golden banner. Also includes 3 French themed in-game avatars.

name: Chinese Dragon Crate
description: A collection of Dragon themed cosmetic items for the Chinese. Equip your units with Dragon Crossbows and Spears, your Shaolin Monk with Iron Fists and wave your Dragon Banner. Lead your empire from the Dragon Palace! Also includes 3 Chinese themed in-game avatars.

name: Aztecs Remnants Crate
description: A collection of Remnants themed cosmetic items for the Aztecs. Equip obsidian maces and shields with fragmented designs. Lead your empire from the Dark Temple and show your might with a Serpent banner. Also includes 3 Aztecs themed in-game avatars.
